{"tid":920960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【龍床盤】菁雋展銷廳首三小時暫收1票 駐場代理：「咁x貴！」","createTime":"2018-11-29T08:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T09:34:39.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ac4e1b8e8f0caacd5568e56a1f70ea119aa8870e","tid":920960,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:12:26.000Z","msg":"【13:55】<br />\n「龍床盤」菁雋今日上午11時開始接受認購登記，現場消息指，首三小時暫收1票。<span style=\"color: red;\">駐場代理直言，「咁x貴，之前吹200萬內，吹低開高」</span>，嚇窒買家。<br />\n<br />\n以貴絕屯門區登場的「龍床盤」菁雋昨日開價後，今日隨即收票。中午12時許，菁雋設於屯門建豐街悅品酒店的展銷廳，記者現場所見，只有大批地產代理撈客，甚少客人入內了解樓盤資訊。看來就算入票金額僅5萬元，較其他新盤約10萬元少一半，都未能刺激買家入票。<br />\n<br />\n全張價單平均呎價高達1.69萬元，成為屯門史上最貴新盤。首張價單共73伙，售價285萬至928.8萬元，呎價13,452元至22,327元。最平單位為8樓32室，實用面積131方呎，價單價285萬元。"},{"pid":"cec65b8a557586da4962eba311fd0f0091280e31","tid":920960,"uid":10692,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:14:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a6687071401fece0cdc8c9019ba99d6058a0c63","tid":920960,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:17:16.000Z","msg":"家陣坐監都有得自僱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6ea489d311e11859d9484e08054fc49f262d66","tid":920960,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:17:20.000Z","msg":"咁撚細不如訓棺材啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b1098733823e646469799d988d5dbac18b5fc0","tid":920960,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:01:16.000Z","msg":"就算唔係買細果個監倉  你一答人住邊 人地都半邊嘴笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67bd6a553f1000c777239d7e7e9af23d5af113be","tid":920960,"uid":12370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:04:31.000Z","msg":"On9先買呢個盤<br />\n咁細賣到兩萬幾尺仲仲要唔係港島<br />\n買左之後要套現仲難過登陸月球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403251fd1f1a1773fd2bfb27046b59c881cb841b","tid":920960,"uid":52006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:06:52.000Z","msg":"285萬劏房會買果個肯定係弱智"},{"pid":"5e32953deeb01f619044300df679fd53f122de86","tid":920960,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2b1098733823e646469799d988d5dbac18b5fc0","tid":920960,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:01:16.000Z","msg":"就算唔係買細果個監倉  你一答人住邊 人地都半邊嘴笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:08:50.000Z","msg":"其實個單位大過我屋企..,"},{"pid":"054dea2de97c1ef4bdc01150258c5b7c067d21c3","tid":920960,"uid":73613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:09:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20c2afc6085fd25b24090868a2f05c9cb3f55db9","tid":920960,"uid":73613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:09:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f41466c95014dc0a7f718cb24ce5ac2b3e7102e","tid":920960,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:10:18.000Z","msg":"龍床盤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0d3d0867d23a433a1f15b616e1bd4c6b8ccc3e","tid":920960,"uid":100766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:11:29.000Z","msg":"冇樓嘅人仍然冇錢買<br />\n有樓嘅人完全唔會買<br />\n<br />\ntarget究竟係啲咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86992dba247db1abd32d8e9ccf36207e772d065","tid":920960,"uid":66769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:12:38.000Z","msg":"買左比人笑到仆街都似 <br />\n<br />\n龍床喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91004e23dfedbeb291e417bc69a94cfcf7ec496","tid":920960,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:34:39.000Z","msg":"打劫坐監都舒適過買呢間野"}]}